snippet.title: Amber Alert for Keyara Collins
snippet.description:
Statewide for the state of Georgia.. Thanks to Metacity for getting me the statement used in the alert..

This mock was remade by me because I did not receive this alert.. Many other people also did not receive this alert, please share this information as soon as possible!!!

Alert Received at 12/26/17 13:44:08 on monitor #4
Matched Filter AMBER CIVIL
The Civil Authorities have issued a Child Abduction Emergency 
for all of Georgia beginning at 1:41 pm and ending at 7:41 pm
(WNGC)
ZCZC-CIV-CAE-013000+0600-3601841-WNGC    -
Alert sent at 12/26/17 13:44:14
The Civil Authorities have issued a Child Abduction Emergency 
for all of Georgia beginning at 1:41 pm and ending at 7:41 pm
(NGAWX/CH)
ZCZC-CIV-CAE-013000+0600-3601841-NGAWX/CH-
Additional log entry:
Alert Received at 12/16/17 13:56:31 on monitor #6
Already heard
Additional TFT log entry:
A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: ALL GEORGIA AT 1:41 PM ON DEC 26 2017 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 7:41 PM.
MESSAGE RECEIVED AT 13:55 ON DEC 26 2017 FROM WWPW ON CHANNEL 3.
EAS PROTOCOL TEXT: ZCZC-CIV-CAE-013000+0600-3601841-WWPW FM
